WEBVTT

01:35.940 --> 01:41.190
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.370 --> 01:43.910
[Episode 12]

01:44.020 --> 01:46.720
[Yixiang Restaurant]

01:48.590 --> 01:50.300
Madam Chen!

01:51.710 --> 01:52.789
You are late.

01:52.789 --> 01:54.850
You must drink a penalty drink later.

01:56.479 --> 01:57.950
Madam Chen.

01:58.280 --> 01:59.630
Madam Liu!

01:59.920 --> 02:02.880
Look at Madam Song's outfit today.

02:03.070 --> 02:05.710
She's looking more and more noble.

02:06.150 --> 02:07.920
I'm flattered, Madam Liu.

02:07.920 --> 02:10.560
It is my honor to be invited

02:10.580 --> 02:12.520
by you ladies today.

02:15.950 --> 02:18.950
It's an imperial green jade bracelet!

02:19.840 --> 02:22.320
This is truly hard to come by.

02:22.520 --> 02:23.840
Look at the transparency

02:23.840 --> 02:24.840
and the color.

02:25.280 --> 02:26.770
It must be worth a lot.

02:27.790 --> 02:28.870
Let's talk while we walk.

02:28.870 --> 02:30.030
Come on.

02:30.079 --> 02:30.960
Let's go.

02:31.400 --> 02:32.510
This bracelet is

02:32.540 --> 02:34.870
a greeting gift
from the Magistrate's wife.

02:34.870 --> 02:36.750
No wonder! So it was a gift
from your in-law.

02:36.750 --> 02:37.690
Yes.

02:38.040 --> 02:39.370
-Oh, my.
-My apologies.

02:39.680 --> 02:41.000
You wretched girl!

02:41.200 --> 02:42.640
You... Why are you here?

02:44.630 --> 02:47.430
You didn't follow me here
just to cause trouble, did you?

02:47.430 --> 02:50.310
What? Did you buy this building?

02:50.590 --> 02:52.120
If you can come, why can't I?

02:52.590 --> 02:53.560
Do you know each other?

02:53.560 --> 02:55.840
No. Who would know her?

02:56.910 --> 02:58.970
Madam Liu, let me tell you something.

02:59.079 --> 03:00.630
My son's marriage was

03:00.630 --> 03:02.560
entirely arranged by the Magistrate.

03:02.560 --> 03:05.010
The Magistrate is from a scholarly family.

03:05.360 --> 03:06.190
-Come often if you like it.
-He values

03:06.190 --> 03:07.520
character and upbringing.

03:07.520 --> 03:10.180
The betrothal gifts
followed ancient customs.

03:10.430 --> 03:13.230
But my daughter-in-law brought
a generous dowry.

03:13.520 --> 03:14.750
Marriage is

03:14.800 --> 03:17.310
all about matching social status.

03:17.310 --> 03:19.640
If the character and upbringing are poor,

03:19.730 --> 03:20.870
such a marriage

03:20.870 --> 03:22.800
-shall never take place.
-Indeed.

03:23.079 --> 03:23.870
Right?

03:24.070 --> 03:26.000
The Magistrate is truly generous.

03:26.280 --> 03:27.280
Congratulations

03:27.400 --> 03:29.910
on selling your Scholar Song
for a good price.

03:29.910 --> 03:30.430
You...

03:30.430 --> 03:31.000
Well...

03:31.810 --> 03:33.040
Wretched girl!

03:36.320 --> 03:37.920
Let's go inside quickly.

03:37.950 --> 03:39.720
Don't let such a vulgar person

03:39.740 --> 03:40.970
ruin our mood.

03:41.000 --> 03:42.360
Right? Come on in.

03:42.380 --> 03:43.650
What is she talking about?

03:43.650 --> 03:45.910
Just nonsense. Forget about it.

03:47.310 --> 03:49.310
Here's a toast to you both.

03:52.910 --> 03:55.120
Manager Yu, you are very experienced

03:55.120 --> 03:56.320
in receiving guests.

03:57.030 --> 03:59.430
It seems you have indeed
met a lot of people.

04:02.240 --> 04:03.890
Our restaurant welcomes guests
from everywhere.

04:03.890 --> 04:05.680
We believe harmony brings wealth.

04:05.680 --> 04:06.800
In business,

04:06.800 --> 04:09.280
it's always good to know more people.

04:12.120 --> 04:14.080
Please make yourselves at home, sirs.

04:14.080 --> 04:16.209
I need to go attend to other guests now.

04:28.510 --> 04:30.310
Manager, what's wrong?

04:30.680 --> 04:31.720
You look pale.

04:33.950 --> 04:36.040
The man in there just touched me.

04:36.680 --> 04:39.250
I don't know why, but that single touch

04:39.750 --> 04:41.590
gave me the creeps.

04:41.950 --> 04:44.010
Another guest who tried to grope you?

04:44.720 --> 04:46.150
How shameless.

04:46.830 --> 04:48.800
It's not really about groping.

04:50.130 --> 04:52.530
I feel like I've seen him
somewhere before.

04:54.040 --> 04:56.770
Who was that young lady
we met at the door just now?

04:57.450 --> 05:00.470
She is called Fan Changyu.

05:01.270 --> 05:04.620
She's a famous disaster
from my hometown, Xigu Lane.

05:04.970 --> 05:06.780
The fortune tellers all say

05:07.000 --> 05:09.870
she is a rare jinx
seen only once in a millennium.

05:10.680 --> 05:12.870
She not only caused her parents' deaths,

05:12.870 --> 05:15.070
but her uncle was also killed
because of her.

05:15.070 --> 05:16.680
It even went to court!

05:16.740 --> 05:17.520
By the way,

05:17.680 --> 05:19.070
just in the middle of this month,

05:19.070 --> 05:21.840
a group of bandits
broke into her home at night,

05:22.270 --> 05:24.310
having killed so many people!

05:24.310 --> 05:27.320
Everyone in Lin'an knows about this.

05:30.600 --> 05:31.790
I wonder

05:32.070 --> 05:34.190
how many people have touched her hands

05:34.190 --> 05:36.710
for her to stay so composed

05:36.830 --> 05:38.190
and feel no shame at all.

05:39.159 --> 05:41.750
I've searched everywhere
all these years, yet I failed to find her.

05:41.750 --> 05:45.159
I didn't expect her to be
doing so well in Lin'an,

05:45.870 --> 05:47.659
and to have met so many men.

05:52.090 --> 05:54.420
Perhaps it's just her business dealings.

05:56.000 --> 05:57.630
You are still making excuses for her.

05:57.630 --> 05:58.770
I dare not.

06:00.000 --> 06:02.510
Back then, she left false clues
about her fleeing beyond the pass,

06:02.510 --> 06:05.110
causing me to search
for her in vain for 6 years.

06:05.750 --> 06:08.790
Never thought she'd establish herself
in just 6 years

06:09.310 --> 06:11.170
and open such a large restaurant.

06:13.070 --> 06:14.870
This woman is really something.

06:15.310 --> 06:16.070
Understood.

06:16.680 --> 06:19.560
I will go investigate
her connections immediately.

06:19.560 --> 06:21.730
Also, investigate the men around her.

06:22.040 --> 06:23.680
For anyone who has touched her,

06:23.680 --> 06:25.940
chop off the parts they touched her with,

06:26.190 --> 06:27.450
and present them to me.

06:29.590 --> 06:30.230
Yes.

06:31.190 --> 06:33.050
I will give the orders right away.

06:36.930 --> 06:39.640
Why would Manager Yu
hire someone like that?

06:39.800 --> 06:41.070
In the restaurant business,

06:41.070 --> 06:42.800
nothing's worse than bad luck.

06:43.240 --> 06:45.040
Perhaps Manager Yu

06:45.040 --> 06:47.170
doesn't know this girl's background,

06:47.310 --> 06:49.370
so she let a jinx in.

06:50.240 --> 06:51.360
Madams.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.140
Manager Yu.

06:52.210 --> 06:54.080
What "jinx"?

06:55.920 --> 06:58.580
We don't have such a dish
at Yixiang Restaurant.

06:58.870 --> 07:00.190
Manager Yu,

07:00.430 --> 07:02.920
we are only looking out
for your best interests.

07:02.920 --> 07:04.190
This jinx

07:04.360 --> 07:06.020
can bring death to people.

07:06.630 --> 07:07.480
Really?

07:08.840 --> 07:10.720
But I heard

07:10.830 --> 07:13.750
that she supported
a scholar fiancé for years.

07:13.800 --> 07:15.350
Once the scholar passed
the provincial exam,

07:15.350 --> 07:17.630
he betrayed her
and broke off the engagement.

07:17.630 --> 07:19.120
In my point of view,

07:19.160 --> 07:21.090
the mother and son are the real ingrates

07:21.090 --> 07:22.040
and jinxes.

07:22.790 --> 07:24.590
They not only harmed the young girl

07:24.590 --> 07:26.090
but also her parents.

07:30.000 --> 07:31.600
So this talk of a jinx

07:31.680 --> 07:34.210
might just be a false rumor.

07:34.750 --> 07:36.350
You're right, Madam Liu.

07:36.870 --> 07:38.110
Mrs. Fan

07:38.140 --> 07:40.190
not only takes care of her sister
all by herself.

07:40.190 --> 07:42.040
Since she joined our Yixiang Restaurant,

07:42.040 --> 07:43.240
my braised meat business

07:43.240 --> 07:44.730
has been booming.

07:45.040 --> 07:46.190
I think

07:46.190 --> 07:48.450
she's actually an auspicious blessing!

07:50.560 --> 07:51.760
However, Madam Song,

07:52.270 --> 07:55.070
who told you she was a jinx?

07:59.220 --> 08:02.380
Just some gossip, I suppose.

08:04.160 --> 08:05.240
Why do women

08:05.260 --> 08:07.240
have to make things hard for other women?

08:07.240 --> 08:09.240
Spouting nonsense and gossiping all day

08:09.240 --> 08:11.240
will bring about God's punishment.

08:12.160 --> 08:13.770
As educated and reasonable
as you are, Madam Song,

08:13.770 --> 08:16.540
how could you gossip
like some filthy trash?

08:16.620 --> 08:18.560
You must have been deceived.

08:24.560 --> 08:26.800
Why are there
still some dishes not served?

08:26.800 --> 08:27.860
I'll go check on them.

08:27.860 --> 08:29.560
Madams, please enjoy the food.

08:29.560 --> 08:30.160
Okay.

08:44.000 --> 08:44.910
You know what?

08:45.120 --> 08:46.520
This manager

08:47.270 --> 08:49.480
got pregnant out of wedlock.

08:49.790 --> 08:51.030
Who knows whose bastard

08:51.030 --> 08:53.390
she carried in her belly?

08:54.720 --> 08:58.480
"Why do women have to make things
hard for other women?" Ridiculous.

08:58.480 --> 08:59.910
I think she's obviously

08:59.910 --> 09:01.340
an immoral slut

09:01.550 --> 09:03.720
just like Fan Changyu.

09:05.670 --> 09:06.610
Let's

09:06.640 --> 09:07.960
not let other people's gossip

09:07.960 --> 09:09.790
ruin our mood.

09:10.000 --> 09:11.010
Yes, exactly.

09:11.120 --> 09:12.650
Let's get back to the point.

09:23.030 --> 09:25.220
A bunch of noisy gossips.

09:25.840 --> 09:27.420
According to them,

09:27.630 --> 09:30.170
the child might be hiding
in this restaurant.

09:33.320 --> 09:34.780
The one who talks the most,

09:35.550 --> 09:36.840
teach her a lesson.

09:40.600 --> 09:41.330
Understood.

09:42.120 --> 09:44.360
-Madam Liu.
-Do you think I'm drunk?

09:44.360 --> 09:45.270
You drank too much.

09:45.270 --> 09:48.200
For this matter,
please put in a good word for me

09:48.510 --> 09:52.570
-in front of your son's father-in-law.
-Don't worry. Just leave it to me.

10:06.470 --> 10:08.490
"Bring about God's punishment"?

10:11.030 --> 10:13.360
I think the one to suffer God's punishment

10:13.440 --> 10:15.840
s-should be that wretched girl!

10:16.000 --> 10:17.480
If God

10:17.480 --> 10:19.160
really sees us all,

10:19.670 --> 10:21.840
He should make that wretched girl...

10:36.490 --> 10:39.510
You'd better think twice
before you speak nonsense

10:40.150 --> 10:41.720
and watch your mouth.

10:42.330 --> 10:43.930
If you spout nonsense again,

10:44.250 --> 10:46.120
it won't end as easily as today.

10:47.060 --> 10:47.810
O-Okay.

10:47.830 --> 10:49.410
I-I get it.

10:53.960 --> 10:54.630
Madam.

10:55.240 --> 10:55.910
Madam!

10:56.790 --> 10:57.440
Madam!

11:08.370 --> 11:09.410
[Braised pork tongue]

11:09.430 --> 11:11.430
[Braised pork belly]

11:11.510 --> 11:17.290
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

11:13.030 --> 11:14.440
Are there any pig ears left?

11:14.440 --> 11:15.440
None left today.

11:15.460 --> 11:17.060
You may come again tomorrow.

11:18.280 --> 11:19.970
It's almost New Year.

11:20.030 --> 11:20.960
Our braised meat is

11:20.960 --> 11:22.150
selling better and better.

11:22.150 --> 11:23.600
You've worked really hard.

11:23.600 --> 11:24.750
You're the one working hard,

11:24.750 --> 11:26.670
busy with so many things every day.

11:26.670 --> 11:28.390
Making money is never easy.

11:29.030 --> 11:30.030
However,

11:30.030 --> 11:32.030
although our braised meat is selling well,

11:32.030 --> 11:34.150
if we want to take it to the next level,

11:34.150 --> 11:36.840
we could design an emblem
for our braised meat.

11:36.910 --> 11:37.720
An emblem?

11:39.030 --> 11:42.460
But my braised meat is
either sliced and served on a plate,

11:42.910 --> 11:45.270
or wrapped in oil paper for takeout.

11:45.550 --> 11:47.000
What's the use of an emblem?

11:47.000 --> 11:48.600
It's exceptionally useful.

11:49.600 --> 11:50.400
Come out here.

11:53.120 --> 11:54.470
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

11:53.480 --> 11:54.320
Look

11:54.790 --> 11:56.760
at these shops downstairs from mine.

11:56.760 --> 11:57.970
Fang's tea,

11:58.000 --> 11:59.080
Li's wine.

11:58.730 --> 11:59.750
[Luo's Pawnshop]

11:59.080 --> 12:00.870
Doesn't every shop have an emblem?

11:59.850 --> 12:00.430
[Fang's Tea Shop]

12:00.430 --> 12:01.220
[Fang]

12:01.080 --> 12:03.210
And each one is unique.

12:01.300 --> 12:02.620
[Li]

12:02.670 --> 12:04.440
[Hua San]

12:03.320 --> 12:05.390
You can tell whose shop it is at a glance.

12:05.390 --> 12:07.550
Later, think of a design for your emblem.

12:07.550 --> 12:09.790
You can make a banner
to hang by the signboard,

12:09.790 --> 12:11.270
so people can see it from afar.

12:11.270 --> 12:12.600
And make some more oil paper.

12:12.600 --> 12:14.270
Print the emblem on the oil paper, too.

12:14.270 --> 12:15.320
When someone buys braised meat,

12:15.320 --> 12:16.420
wrap it in that oil paper.

12:16.420 --> 12:18.750
Your fame will surely surpass the Wang's.

12:19.360 --> 12:20.000
I got it.

12:20.270 --> 12:22.240
I'll find you

12:22.240 --> 12:23.870
a scholar with nice handwriting.

12:23.870 --> 12:25.550
Let's get this done today.

12:26.330 --> 12:27.080
Qianqian.

12:26.540 --> 12:27.810
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

12:27.960 --> 12:30.270
My husband can write as well.

12:30.440 --> 12:31.840
I'll just ask him to help.

12:32.240 --> 12:35.020
How is your husband's handwriting?

12:35.240 --> 12:36.200
Excellent.

12:36.870 --> 12:37.670
Really.

12:39.000 --> 12:40.930
Even more beautiful than his face.

12:42.080 --> 12:43.480
That impressive?

12:43.790 --> 12:45.480
Then he must be as great
as the legendary calligraphers,

12:45.480 --> 12:46.840
Wang Xizhi and Zhong Yao!

12:46.840 --> 12:47.630
Wang Xi...

12:51.180 --> 12:54.080
I don't know who those two are,

12:54.630 --> 12:56.430
but I think he's about that good.

12:57.270 --> 12:58.270
Changyu,

12:58.670 --> 12:59.960
I really love

13:00.030 --> 13:01.320
your personality.

13:02.020 --> 13:05.710
[Fan]

13:08.670 --> 13:11.150
Sir, your handwriting is truly elegant.

13:11.270 --> 13:12.960
-Yes.
-Having worked here for years,

13:12.960 --> 13:14.510
I've never seen anyone's handwriting

13:14.510 --> 13:16.550
as good as yours, sir.

13:16.590 --> 13:17.710
Truly amazing.

13:17.840 --> 13:20.040
-It's so well written.
-Manager, look.

13:22.100 --> 13:23.560
[Fan]

13:23.870 --> 13:25.030
It's so beautiful.

13:26.960 --> 13:28.420
Do you want to take a break?

13:28.920 --> 13:30.560
No need. I'll keep writing.

13:31.120 --> 13:31.870
Changyu.

13:32.790 --> 13:34.590
Your husband's handwriting...

13:35.080 --> 13:36.420
It's really good!

13:37.380 --> 13:39.040
Much better than that Wang...

13:40.030 --> 13:41.840
Wang something.

13:41.840 --> 13:44.600
Fine. Beauty is in the eye
of the beholder.

13:44.600 --> 13:45.600
Of course it's good.

13:45.600 --> 13:48.270
Yes. No matter what Zheng writes or draws,

13:48.270 --> 13:50.060
I think it's the best.

13:51.030 --> 13:53.030
Fuling, take Changning upstairs
to have some goodies.

13:53.030 --> 13:54.690
You can eat whatever you want.

13:54.790 --> 13:56.390
Thank you, Fairy Sister.

13:56.870 --> 13:58.150
That's so sweet.

13:58.440 --> 13:59.040
Off you go.

14:02.550 --> 14:03.510
Changyu,

14:03.670 --> 14:04.840
you really found yourself

14:04.840 --> 14:07.170
a husband good with both brains and brawn.

14:07.270 --> 14:08.670
Thank you for the compliment.

14:08.670 --> 14:09.730
No need to thank me.

14:10.390 --> 14:11.670
From today on,

14:11.840 --> 14:13.670
we must stick together.

14:13.790 --> 14:15.480
Show those gossips

14:15.630 --> 14:18.490
that we young women are
also capable of great deeds!

14:21.270 --> 14:26.850
[Fan]

14:24.960 --> 14:27.150
-I want some, too!
-I also want some!

14:26.990 --> 14:29.350
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

14:27.150 --> 14:29.750
Me too! I want one!

14:34.760 --> 14:37.990
[Fan]

14:40.720 --> 14:42.480
Qianqian, you're so insightful.

14:42.480 --> 14:44.140
You said drawing these things

14:44.200 --> 14:46.360
would attract a lot of people,
and it really did!

14:46.360 --> 14:47.870
You're mistaken.

14:48.030 --> 14:49.440
The real attraction is

14:49.440 --> 14:50.880
your husband.

14:52.160 --> 14:54.380
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

15:03.630 --> 15:04.960
Why are you still standing there?

15:04.960 --> 15:05.960
Go help him.

15:06.550 --> 15:07.440
Go, go, go.

15:14.200 --> 15:15.030
I'll help you.

15:19.120 --> 15:19.850
Here you are.

15:25.320 --> 15:27.050
Isn't this the meat you wanted?

15:34.960 --> 15:36.360
This was just wrapped up.

15:36.630 --> 15:37.320
Yes.

15:40.150 --> 15:41.320
Is what he takes different?

15:41.320 --> 15:43.650
Yes, the meat he hands over smells better.

15:45.550 --> 15:46.840
-I want some, too!
-I also want some!

15:46.840 --> 15:47.940
Give it to me! Me!

15:50.840 --> 15:53.030
That's mine! Give it to me!
I want some, too!

15:53.030 --> 15:53.910
Here you are.

15:54.270 --> 15:55.150
Here.

15:59.080 --> 16:02.380
You can do it.

16:02.510 --> 16:05.580
Come on.

16:07.080 --> 16:09.080
It's fine. It's okay.

16:12.360 --> 16:13.960
You weighed this wrong.

16:15.840 --> 16:17.010
No rush, sir.

16:17.200 --> 16:18.200
No need to rush.

16:28.030 --> 16:29.090
It's underweight.

16:29.240 --> 16:30.370
I cut an extra piece.

16:31.480 --> 16:32.210
Here you are.

16:41.360 --> 16:42.720
What does it have to do with you?

16:42.720 --> 16:44.000
Stay out of this.

16:47.480 --> 16:50.840
-I want some, too!
-I also want some!

16:50.870 --> 16:52.270
-Me, too.
-Any meat left?

16:54.150 --> 16:55.810
I shouldn't have let you come.

17:00.830 --> 17:04.270
-Give it to me. I'll pay double the price.
-I also want some!

17:04.270 --> 17:06.109
-I want some, too.
-Me, too.

17:10.410 --> 17:18.030
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

17:19.069 --> 17:20.069
Is there any left?

17:20.440 --> 17:21.270
Sorry, sir.

17:21.270 --> 17:22.670
We're sold out for today.

17:23.550 --> 17:25.150
What about those in the back?

17:25.270 --> 17:26.480
Those are just scraps.

17:26.480 --> 17:27.680
Scraps are fine, too.

17:27.680 --> 17:29.210
Are you selling them or not?

17:29.440 --> 17:30.900
Yes. If you pay, I'll sell.

17:30.960 --> 17:31.880
Here, take it.

17:34.960 --> 17:36.200
Your hands are greasy.

17:36.200 --> 17:38.400
Be careful not to dirty the paper on top.

17:46.260 --> 17:46.820
[Fan]

17:48.550 --> 17:50.130
This calligraphy is brilliant.

17:50.130 --> 17:51.390
Using it to wrap meat is

17:51.680 --> 17:53.160
squandering a treasure.

17:54.070 --> 17:54.720
[Fan]

17:55.230 --> 17:55.990
Really nice.

17:59.160 --> 18:01.070
"Squandering a treasure"?

18:03.070 --> 18:04.270
What does that mean?

18:09.240 --> 18:10.040
Let's pack up.

18:13.560 --> 18:18.230
[Welcome guests from far and wide]

18:16.680 --> 18:18.000
I'm not drunk.

18:22.480 --> 18:23.640
Take care, Mr. Wu.

18:25.480 --> 18:26.640
Qianqian.

18:28.070 --> 18:29.680
Go wait for me in the carriage.

18:29.680 --> 18:31.480
Did you enjoy your drink, Mr. Wu?

18:31.830 --> 18:34.030
It's getting late. It's time to go home.

18:34.880 --> 18:36.710
Why go home?

18:38.000 --> 18:39.600
Everyone knows I am

18:40.110 --> 18:41.950
a regular here.

18:42.400 --> 18:43.460
-Mr. Wu.
-Let's go.

18:43.480 --> 18:44.640
Drink a few more cups with me.

18:44.640 --> 18:46.880
I'm doing this for your own good.

18:47.070 --> 18:48.880
If you go back late,

18:48.880 --> 18:50.000
Mrs. Wu will come cause trouble

18:50.000 --> 18:51.930
for our Yixiang Restaurant again.

18:56.240 --> 18:58.880
Don't use that fierce woman
to pressure me.

18:58.920 --> 19:00.210
Listen carefully.

19:00.400 --> 19:02.740
If you don't keep me good company today,

19:02.760 --> 19:05.820
don't expect to keep this place
running smoothly.

19:05.920 --> 19:08.110
Mr. Wu, please mind your manners.

19:08.550 --> 19:09.240
Go away!

19:11.550 --> 19:14.240
How dare you, a maid,
talk to me like that?

19:14.680 --> 19:15.830
-Who taught you to do that?
-Mr. Wu!

19:15.830 --> 19:16.400
Mr. Wu.

19:16.400 --> 19:17.240
Calm down, please.

19:17.240 --> 19:18.510
I'll drink with you.

19:20.440 --> 19:21.440
Bring the cups.

19:28.880 --> 19:29.550
Cheers.

19:36.420 --> 19:37.370
How dare you,

19:37.880 --> 19:39.440
a scoundrel, run wild here?

19:39.550 --> 19:41.270
I've dealt with countless men like you.

19:41.270 --> 19:42.160
Send him back to the Wu's Mansion

19:42.160 --> 19:43.200
and hand him over to Mrs. Wu!

19:43.200 --> 19:43.790
Yes.

19:45.000 --> 19:45.680
Let go!

19:46.240 --> 19:47.790
Who do you think you are?

19:48.310 --> 19:50.070
Let go! Let go of me!

19:50.590 --> 19:51.980
Do you know who I am?

20:00.440 --> 20:01.280
Bitch!

20:45.830 --> 20:46.890
Are you alright?

20:59.920 --> 21:01.070
Here you are, Mr. Qi.

21:05.790 --> 21:07.720
Master, what should we do with him?

21:09.480 --> 21:11.000
Do as Manager Yu said.

21:11.200 --> 21:13.600
Send him back
to Mrs. Wu at the Wu's Mansion.

21:13.790 --> 21:16.200
Remember, send him back alive.

21:17.440 --> 21:19.440
Don't cause trouble for Manager Yu.

21:19.550 --> 21:20.680
-Yes!
-Understood.

21:31.960 --> 21:34.750
Manager Yu, you look pale.

21:36.910 --> 21:38.570
Were you frightened just now?

21:44.070 --> 21:44.750
I'm fine.

21:46.130 --> 21:47.880
Thank you for saving me, Mr. Qi.

22:00.640 --> 22:01.350
Farewell.

22:53.510 --> 22:55.640
Manager, are you okay?

23:02.240 --> 23:03.900
He behaves a bit like that guy,

23:04.640 --> 23:06.370
but there's no scar on his face.

23:08.040 --> 23:09.840
And the voice is different, too.

23:11.750 --> 23:13.010
Don't scare yourself.

23:13.480 --> 23:15.050
Why would he come to Lin'an?

23:15.550 --> 23:16.510
Who?

23:19.810 --> 23:20.530
Nothing.

23:27.760 --> 23:29.800
[Permeating fragrance]

23:28.000 --> 23:29.680
These snacks are all for you.

23:30.030 --> 23:31.880
My sister can really eat as well.

23:32.240 --> 23:34.310
She eats enough for 3 meals
in one sitting,

23:34.310 --> 23:36.510
with her rice bowl as big
as a soup tureen.

23:36.510 --> 23:38.440
Your sister is impressive!

23:38.750 --> 23:40.680
Have you ever seen a pig slaughter?

23:40.920 --> 23:41.680
No.

23:42.350 --> 23:43.760
My sister can knock a pig out

23:43.760 --> 23:45.920
with one single slap.

23:47.110 --> 23:47.890
Really?

23:48.000 --> 23:48.720
I've never seen anyone

23:48.720 --> 23:50.380
as formidable as your sister.

23:50.960 --> 23:53.130
Fuling, come over and help!

23:53.960 --> 23:55.650
I'm going out for a bit.

23:55.940 --> 23:57.160
I'll be right back.

24:41.200 --> 24:42.110
Thief!

24:42.590 --> 24:44.200
I... I'm not a thief.

24:44.270 --> 24:45.360
I don't care who you are.

24:45.360 --> 24:46.550
You are stealing food.

24:46.550 --> 24:48.830
I'm going to tell my sister
and the Fairy Sister.

24:48.830 --> 24:49.440
Don't!

24:49.440 --> 24:51.590
Changyu, someone is stealing food!

24:53.110 --> 24:54.480
Don't, please don't!

24:54.480 --> 24:56.070
It's all because you're stealing food!

24:56.070 --> 24:57.200
This is my home.

24:57.200 --> 24:59.110
My mother owns this restaurant.

24:59.160 --> 25:00.600
Why can't I eat it?

25:00.680 --> 25:03.110
You are the Fairy Sister's son?

25:03.770 --> 25:06.280
What's your name? How old are you?

25:07.270 --> 25:09.400
I'm Yu Bao'er. I'm 6.

25:09.400 --> 25:10.260
What about you?

25:10.640 --> 25:12.000
Try this piece.

25:12.200 --> 25:13.830
Just this piece is enough for me.

25:13.830 --> 25:15.450
Mother doesn't let me eat too much.

25:15.450 --> 25:17.910
She says too many sweets cause cavities.

25:18.640 --> 25:19.970
What are cavities?

25:20.310 --> 25:21.430
They're like...

25:24.790 --> 25:26.960
Little worms will eat your teeth.

25:27.160 --> 25:28.750
It hurts so much.

25:28.920 --> 25:30.470
Worms will grow?

25:30.830 --> 25:33.920
Like cabbage worms or rice weevils?

25:34.270 --> 25:35.470
I don't know, either.

25:35.580 --> 25:36.800
I've never had them.

25:37.350 --> 25:39.210
Then we'd better not eat anymore.

25:40.250 --> 25:42.380
How about we go play outside together?

25:44.050 --> 25:45.910
Mother says I have a special fate,

25:46.200 --> 25:48.000
and I should avoid seeing too many people.

25:48.000 --> 25:48.800
Only then...

25:49.220 --> 25:50.620
Only then can I stay safe.

25:53.480 --> 25:56.590
Then let's play hide-and-seek.

26:13.160 --> 26:14.290
You can't take this.

26:15.160 --> 26:16.290
-Kids...
-Go away.

26:16.310 --> 26:17.520
-Sorry.
-I'm sorry.

26:26.660 --> 26:27.580
Bao'er?

26:28.550 --> 26:29.750
Why are you here?

26:29.790 --> 26:30.830
-This way.
-Let's go.

26:30.830 --> 26:32.960
Your mother told you not to run around!

26:34.240 --> 26:36.030
You two. Don't touch it.

26:46.030 --> 26:47.370
It doesn't matter.

26:47.440 --> 26:49.640
-Just a moment.
-OK, I'll go back later.

26:51.790 --> 26:53.520
Where did you come from, brats?

26:53.720 --> 26:55.450
You spoiled my mood. Get out.

26:55.830 --> 26:57.310
You're still running here?

26:57.310 --> 26:58.000
Stop!

26:58.350 --> 26:59.030
Run!

27:00.080 --> 27:02.040
You brats, how dare you ruin my day?

27:02.070 --> 27:02.960
Get lost!

27:10.680 --> 27:11.440
Changning?

27:12.400 --> 27:13.270
Changning!

27:28.750 --> 27:29.610
She's not here.

27:52.640 --> 27:54.920
I'll go in and light the lamps
for you two first.

27:54.920 --> 27:57.050
No need to light the lamps in this room.

27:57.240 --> 27:59.720
Arrange the wine and dishes
the same as on our first day here.

27:59.720 --> 28:00.350
Got it.

28:17.270 --> 28:18.270
Keep this in mind.

28:19.310 --> 28:20.800
No matter when or where,

28:21.680 --> 28:23.610
never make decisions on my behalf,

28:24.750 --> 28:26.550
even if we kill the wrong person.

28:28.160 --> 28:29.290
Do you understand?

28:30.640 --> 28:31.270
Yes.

28:34.400 --> 28:36.400
I'm so sleepy.

28:36.400 --> 28:37.610
Shh. Be quiet.

28:38.790 --> 28:40.590
How is the investigation going?

28:42.160 --> 28:43.510
I've asked around.

28:44.380 --> 28:46.580
Based on the time she arrived in Lin'an,

28:47.070 --> 28:50.470
the child was very likely conceived
in the Prince's Mansion.

28:50.830 --> 28:53.590
To confirm her identity
with absolute certainty,

28:53.590 --> 28:56.720
we need the Nanny to come to Lin'an
to verify it in person.

29:07.880 --> 29:09.140
Then go arrange it now.

29:09.920 --> 29:11.320
I'll get on it right away.

29:12.200 --> 29:12.930
Who's there?

29:26.070 --> 29:27.680
Sold out so early?

29:28.440 --> 29:29.240
All sold out for today.

29:29.240 --> 29:30.840
Please come again tomorrow.

29:30.960 --> 29:31.480
Okay.

29:40.680 --> 29:41.310
Make way.

29:42.400 --> 29:43.070
Move.

29:44.960 --> 29:47.790
Mr. Li, where are these soldiers from?

29:48.960 --> 29:51.160
Advisor Guo,
who freeloaded here yesterday, said

29:51.160 --> 29:53.840
the front lines are in trouble,
so they're requisitioning grain again.

29:53.840 --> 29:54.720
Looks like

29:55.640 --> 29:57.680
these soldiers are here for the grain.

29:57.680 --> 29:59.680
Wei Xuan's bound to be defeated.

29:59.790 --> 30:03.590
I just didn't expect that he couldn't even
hold on until the New Year.

30:06.960 --> 30:07.880
I also heard

30:08.550 --> 30:10.240
that in Chongzhou,
in order to collect grain,

30:10.240 --> 30:11.960
they drove farmers to their deaths.

30:11.960 --> 30:13.640
They all say Mr. He in our Jizhou is

30:13.640 --> 30:15.240
a just and upright official.

30:15.240 --> 30:16.790
I hope he won't be like those
in Chongzhou,

30:16.790 --> 30:18.030
just to collect grain,

30:18.030 --> 30:20.430
driving the common people to their deaths.

30:21.920 --> 30:25.180
It all depends on
how the Jizhou Government will handle it.

30:32.310 --> 30:33.240
What is this for?

30:34.000 --> 30:34.660
It's yours.

30:36.350 --> 30:37.880
I don't need it. You keep it.

30:38.750 --> 30:39.720
No.

30:40.440 --> 30:41.500
Half for each of us.

30:41.640 --> 30:43.700
You wrote hundreds of paper packets.

30:44.640 --> 30:46.200
I might lose it if I carry it.

30:47.280 --> 30:48.370
You keep it for me.

30:52.440 --> 30:54.680
Fine. I'll keep it for you.

30:56.070 --> 30:56.590
Okay.

31:00.030 --> 31:01.430
Have you seen Changning?

31:03.480 --> 31:04.480
She's missing.

31:05.440 --> 31:07.770
Those goddamn bandits are after us again?

31:11.030 --> 31:12.110
-Bao'er!
-Changning!

31:12.110 --> 31:12.680
Bao'er!

31:12.680 --> 31:13.590
Who is Bao'er?

31:13.720 --> 31:14.550
My son.

31:15.960 --> 31:16.550
Fuling!

31:17.400 --> 31:18.110
Fuling!

31:18.680 --> 31:20.640
Manager, Bao'er isn't in the secret room.

31:20.640 --> 31:22.000
Changning was just here.

31:22.000 --> 31:23.240
I went out for a bit,

31:23.240 --> 31:24.270
and she's gone.

31:25.720 --> 31:26.510
Qi...

31:27.070 --> 31:28.450
It must be him.

31:28.510 --> 31:29.660
Who is Qi?

31:29.920 --> 31:31.320
That man comes every day.

31:31.510 --> 31:32.200
Every time I see him,

31:32.200 --> 31:33.510
I get goosebumps.

31:33.510 --> 31:34.960
He must be the one who took Bao'er away!

31:34.960 --> 31:36.420
Let's split up and search.

31:36.440 --> 31:37.030
Okay.

31:41.350 --> 31:42.440
Has that guest surnamed Qi left?

31:42.440 --> 31:43.650
I-I don't know.

31:46.240 --> 31:48.000
Manager, please calm down.

31:49.350 --> 31:50.550
Where is that guy surnamed Qi?

31:50.550 --> 31:51.950
He just left not long ago.

31:52.920 --> 31:54.880
Did he have anyone with him when he left?

31:54.880 --> 31:56.420
He left in a hurry.

31:56.510 --> 31:57.370
I didn't notice

31:57.400 --> 31:58.940
whether he had anyone with him.

31:58.940 --> 31:59.640
-Manager!
-Manager!

31:59.640 --> 32:00.700
Calm down, please!

32:11.920 --> 32:13.380
Manager, are you alright?

32:14.070 --> 32:14.790
How is your hand?

32:14.790 --> 32:15.720
Let me see.

32:45.240 --> 32:46.640
I'll get on it right away.

32:47.350 --> 32:48.080
Who's there?

32:49.440 --> 32:51.000
Sir, it's me.

32:57.390 --> 32:58.920
Sorry, sir.

32:59.070 --> 33:01.070
I accidentally knocked over
the lampstand just now.

33:01.070 --> 33:02.070
Did I disturb you?

33:02.440 --> 33:03.170
Give it to me.

33:03.680 --> 33:04.350
You can go now.

33:04.350 --> 33:05.280
Enjoy your meal.

33:11.150 --> 33:17.860
[Heaven-class]

33:15.680 --> 33:17.030
How have I taught you?

33:18.310 --> 33:20.170
I... I dare not forget, Mother.

33:21.200 --> 33:21.920
I was just...

33:21.920 --> 33:22.750
Just what?

33:23.440 --> 33:24.640
Just playing around?

33:26.680 --> 33:27.750
Do you just let everything

33:27.750 --> 33:29.240
I usually tell you go in one ear
and out the other?

33:29.240 --> 33:30.200
Why won't you listen?

33:30.200 --> 33:31.460
Why are you so playful?

33:35.350 --> 33:37.240
Qianqian, your hand is hurt.

33:37.640 --> 33:39.700
Why don't you go apply some medicine?

33:41.020 --> 33:45.550
[Heaven-class]

33:43.220 --> 33:45.670
Fairy Sister, please don't be mad.

33:46.160 --> 33:47.960
It's my fault. I fell asleep.

33:48.240 --> 33:50.470
Bao'er was just keeping me company.

33:52.880 --> 33:54.000
I won't blame you.

33:54.640 --> 33:57.580
Can I come play with Bao'er again
in the future?

34:08.280 --> 34:09.940
Get up now. The ground is cold.

34:14.230 --> 34:14.980
Mother.

34:14.909 --> 34:17.730
[Heaven-class]

34:20.110 --> 34:22.550
Qianqian is usually so nice to everyone.

34:23.150 --> 34:25.750
But why does she treat her own son
like an enemy?

34:25.800 --> 34:27.030
Her reaction today was

34:27.030 --> 34:28.830
indeed more fearful than yours.

34:30.480 --> 34:32.139
I'm going back to check on her.

34:32.710 --> 34:35.030
Even close friends have their secrets.

34:35.400 --> 34:37.330
She will tell you when she wants to.

34:38.070 --> 34:40.330
I wonder what Qianqian has been through.

34:44.230 --> 34:46.760
Changyu, I'm sleepy.

34:48.360 --> 34:49.230
She's sleepy.

34:52.510 --> 34:53.639
Come on, Changning.

34:57.440 --> 34:58.230
Hold onto me.

35:05.040 --> 35:09.360
[He]

35:09.470 --> 35:16.730
[Peace at the border]

35:09.700 --> 35:11.780
In our Great Yin's 1 capital city
and 17 prefectures,

35:11.780 --> 35:13.710
the Northwest comprises 4 of them.

35:13.920 --> 35:16.580
Jinzhou is barren,
and Chongzhou has rebelled.

35:16.840 --> 35:19.770
That leaves only 2 prefectures,
Jizhou and Yanzhou.

35:20.230 --> 35:21.070
Yanzhou is

35:21.890 --> 35:23.170
a garrison post.

35:24.110 --> 35:26.110
The Imperial Court strictly forbids
hoarding grain or farming there.

35:26.110 --> 35:28.070
That means right now in the Northwest,

35:28.070 --> 35:30.600
only our Jizhou prefecture
can supply grain.

35:31.480 --> 35:32.610
Wei Xuan

35:33.360 --> 35:35.280
clearly thinks the fire of war
in Chongzhou is

35:35.280 --> 35:36.570
not raging enough.

35:37.030 --> 35:40.460
Wei Xuan sent troops
to requisition grain by force.

35:40.550 --> 35:43.210
The soldiers even took the seeds
farmers kept.

35:43.630 --> 35:46.040
Forget about spring planting
of the common people.

35:45.680 --> 35:49.370
[He]

35:46.320 --> 35:49.680
It'll already be a blessing for them
to just survive the harsh winter.

35:49.680 --> 35:50.800
Doing this is

35:50.880 --> 35:52.590
like digging our own grave!

35:56.360 --> 35:58.490
Why couldn't we collect enough grain?

35:59.400 --> 36:00.860
I've had it investigated.

36:01.360 --> 36:02.150
A month ago,

36:02.150 --> 36:03.510
a group of merchants from out of town

36:03.510 --> 36:05.280
bought up grain everywhere at high prices.

36:05.280 --> 36:07.800
The people only kept seeds
and coarse grain for themselves,

36:07.800 --> 36:09.030
and sold all the rest.

36:09.510 --> 36:11.030
Buying grain in wartime.

36:11.760 --> 36:14.490
Go investigate these merchants
from out of town.

36:14.880 --> 36:16.610
-Yes, General.
-Yes, General.

36:19.100 --> 36:20.760
Your Lordship, I've figured it out.

36:20.760 --> 36:22.190
The one who bought grain in the city is

36:22.190 --> 36:23.630
the manager of Lin'an Rice Shop,

36:23.630 --> 36:24.490
named Zhao Xun.

36:26.630 --> 36:28.280
He united grain merchants from many places

36:28.280 --> 36:30.000
to buy grain at high prices
in Yanzhou and Jizhou,

36:30.000 --> 36:31.860
totaling nearly 200,000 piculs.

36:32.590 --> 36:33.640
Zhao Xun?

36:37.670 --> 36:39.840
Has he been
closely interacting with someone recently?

36:39.840 --> 36:42.440
Yes, someone who claimed
to be a rice merchant from the Capital,

36:42.440 --> 36:43.400
surnamed Qi.

36:44.710 --> 36:45.670
Qi?

36:48.590 --> 36:49.480
Mr. Qi,

36:49.760 --> 36:52.000
our manager hasn't recovered
from her cold yet.

36:52.000 --> 36:53.800
She has been resting behind closed doors

36:53.800 --> 36:55.760
and really can't see anyone.

36:56.190 --> 36:57.990
Hope you can understand it, sir.

37:00.360 --> 37:01.610
If it's a cold,

37:02.280 --> 37:03.040
why didn't she accept

37:03.040 --> 37:05.320
the medicine I had a famous doctor
prescribe for her?

37:05.320 --> 37:07.190
She didn't even accept the fox-fur coat.

37:07.190 --> 37:08.790
Is it not warm enough for her?

37:10.070 --> 37:11.070
Or is it that

37:11.630 --> 37:13.830
your manager is avoiding me on purpose?

37:14.760 --> 37:15.550
No way.

37:15.920 --> 37:18.000
Our manager doesn't mean to slight you.

37:18.000 --> 37:19.750
She is just seriously ill.

37:21.030 --> 37:22.150
How serious?

37:23.070 --> 37:24.530
She's not dead yet, is she?

37:27.070 --> 37:28.000
Tell her,

37:28.440 --> 37:31.070
I always get to see the person
I want to see.

37:36.280 --> 37:38.000
So it's you, Mr. Qi! Welcome.

37:38.280 --> 37:40.320
Go serve the dishes. The best ones.

37:41.000 --> 37:41.590
Yes.

37:45.400 --> 37:47.130
Serve the most expensive ones.

37:50.000 --> 37:51.200
It seems you're fine.

37:59.550 --> 38:00.670
It's just a cold.

38:00.800 --> 38:01.800
Nothing serious.

38:02.710 --> 38:05.800
Besides, the physician said
it's more important to keep inner peace.

38:05.800 --> 38:07.490
Don't get angry or sad,

38:07.880 --> 38:09.280
and avoid looking at disgusting things.

38:09.280 --> 38:10.740
That helps with recovery.

38:18.480 --> 38:19.140
Don't move.

38:20.970 --> 38:22.070
Men and women aren't supposed to
get intimate.

38:22.070 --> 38:23.930
Please show some respect, Mr. Qi.

38:24.070 --> 38:25.130
I said, don't move.

38:39.710 --> 38:41.030
Your pulse was slow just now.

38:41.030 --> 38:42.430
It's indeed like a chill.

38:43.440 --> 38:45.480
But now it has quickened a lot.

38:54.070 --> 38:56.320
This medicine is exactly what you need.

38:59.480 --> 39:00.480
Thank you, Mr. Qi.

39:01.360 --> 39:04.000
Manager Yu, you seem
to dislike me so much.

39:09.030 --> 39:10.510
What are you talking about?

39:10.510 --> 39:12.360
It's not that I dislike you.

39:12.880 --> 39:14.710
It's just that I haven't recovered
from my cold,

39:14.710 --> 39:16.320
and I'm afraid I'll spoil your mood

39:16.320 --> 39:17.980
for enjoying the delicacies.

39:18.760 --> 39:20.090
I'll take my leave then.

39:25.400 --> 39:26.530
Where are you going?

39:27.590 --> 39:28.800
None of your business.

39:28.800 --> 39:30.230
I wanted you to take the medicine

39:30.230 --> 39:31.480
for your own good.

39:32.550 --> 39:34.510
There are plenty of men who care about me.

39:34.510 --> 39:35.370
Go wait in line.

39:37.030 --> 39:37.840
Who are they?

39:39.190 --> 39:40.130
Let go.

39:40.400 --> 39:41.110
Let go of me!

39:42.110 --> 39:43.170
What are you doing?

39:43.840 --> 39:46.710
Mr. Qi's concern for Manager Yu is

39:46.710 --> 39:48.260
truly a grand gesture.

39:48.480 --> 39:50.670
He actually booked
the entire Yixiang Restaurant.

39:50.670 --> 39:51.360
Manager Yu,

39:51.800 --> 39:53.440
now you can have a good rest.

39:56.030 --> 39:57.960
You booked my Yixiang Restaurant?

39:58.070 --> 39:59.280
Manager Zhao just said

39:59.280 --> 40:01.000
he'd offer 100 taels a day

40:01.000 --> 40:02.550
to book the Yixiang Restaurant
for 10 days.

40:02.550 --> 40:03.480
Ten days.

40:04.030 --> 40:05.480
I'm booking everything

40:06.150 --> 40:07.680
in the Yixiang Restaurant.

40:11.070 --> 40:13.030
Only 100 taels a day?

40:14.150 --> 40:15.970
Did you not bring enough money?

40:16.230 --> 40:17.510
At least 1,000 taels a day.

40:17.510 --> 40:18.400
Not a wen less.

40:19.150 --> 40:20.350
Do you have that much?

40:22.800 --> 40:23.800
Just this little?

40:29.210 --> 40:32.850
[Yixiang Restaurant]

40:31.320 --> 40:32.360
That's strange.

40:32.400 --> 40:33.510
How weird.

40:34.340 --> 40:36.350
The Manager didn't notify us.

40:39.190 --> 40:41.630
-Excuse me.
-The Restaurant is closed to reorganize.

40:41.630 --> 40:43.840
We appreciate your understanding.

40:42.930 --> 40:46.340
[The Restaurant is closed to reorganize.
We appreciate your understanding.]

40:47.110 --> 40:48.840
Why is it closed all of a sudden?

40:49.000 --> 40:50.130
Where is Manager Yu?

40:50.840 --> 40:52.360
We also came to work early this morning

40:52.360 --> 40:53.630
and just found out.

40:53.920 --> 40:55.450
We haven't seen Manager Yu.

40:56.110 --> 40:57.000
This is weird.

40:59.400 --> 41:00.710
Madam Man, Mr. Li.

41:01.110 --> 41:02.760
Why is the Yixiang Restaurant closed?

41:02.760 --> 41:04.420
Mr. Qi booked the whole place.

41:04.480 --> 41:06.220
He sent us back to rest for a few days,

41:06.220 --> 41:07.590
saying he doesn't need us to serve.

41:07.590 --> 41:08.720
It's weird, though.

41:08.760 --> 41:09.960
Even the doors are all locked.

41:09.960 --> 41:11.190
In all my years at the Yixiang Restaurant,

41:11.190 --> 41:12.730
I've never seen this happen before.

41:12.730 --> 41:13.490
Indeed.

41:14.150 --> 41:15.080
Where is Qianqian?

41:15.080 --> 41:16.000
She was sick yesterday,

41:16.000 --> 41:17.000
so she must be inside now.

41:17.000 --> 41:17.720
Yes.

41:18.920 --> 41:19.980
I'll go take a look.

41:20.400 --> 41:21.360
The doors are locked.

41:21.360 --> 41:23.760
You're not actually thinking of flying...

41:28.440 --> 41:29.770
She actually flew over.

41:33.880 --> 41:34.630
Qianqian!

41:36.480 --> 41:37.190
Qianqian!

41:39.150 --> 41:40.150
-Qianqian!
-Don't come over!

41:40.150 --> 41:40.960
Help!

41:42.000 --> 41:43.760
Don't come over. Stay back.

41:46.320 --> 41:47.380
-Qianqian.
-No...

41:47.660 --> 41:48.420
No.

41:49.780 --> 41:50.710
-No!
-Qianqian.

41:51.070 --> 41:51.680
Get lost!

41:52.190 --> 41:53.540
-Qianqian.
-Go away!

41:54.880 --> 41:55.700
No!

41:55.880 --> 41:56.590
No!

41:58.760 --> 41:59.400
Changyu...

41:59.400 --> 42:00.290
It's okay.

42:04.280 --> 42:05.190
What's wrong?

42:05.320 --> 42:06.070
What dream did you have

42:06.070 --> 42:07.200
to scare you so much?

42:09.200 --> 42:10.770
I dreamed of a madman.

42:14.880 --> 42:15.810
Go away!

42:15.830 --> 42:17.280
A masked madman.

42:25.440 --> 42:26.170
Here you are.

42:29.510 --> 42:30.800
Madam Man said the Yixiang Restaurant was

42:30.800 --> 42:32.700
booked by Mr. Qi.

42:33.110 --> 42:34.190
What's going on?

42:38.550 --> 42:39.230
No.

42:40.110 --> 42:42.110
I didn't dare take on this business.

42:43.400 --> 42:44.190
Why?

42:45.230 --> 42:47.110
I deliberately asked for 1,000 taels,

42:47.110 --> 42:48.400
but he still agreed.

42:49.800 --> 42:51.550
The more I thought about it,
the more scared I got.

42:51.550 --> 42:54.150
So I just closed up the restaurant
to avoid him.

42:56.710 --> 42:58.280
Is it possible

42:58.760 --> 43:00.770
that he just likes you?

43:06.070 --> 43:07.070
I don't know.

43:08.510 --> 43:10.230
I just feel like

43:10.840 --> 43:12.040
it's not that simple.

43:14.150 --> 43:15.880
How about I tie him up in a sack,

43:15.880 --> 43:16.630
beat him up,

43:16.630 --> 43:17.830
and ask what he wants?

43:18.800 --> 43:21.110
Beating people up isn't
a long-term solution.

43:21.110 --> 43:23.280
Isn't Butcher Guo the best example?

43:24.480 --> 43:27.080
Besides,
booking a restaurant isn't illegal.

43:29.630 --> 43:30.630
That makes sense.

43:31.800 --> 43:33.800
Why is this clingy guy so annoying?

43:35.280 --> 43:38.480
I've seen enough
of this domineering, big-spending act.

43:40.000 --> 43:41.920
If he really just likes me,

43:42.400 --> 43:44.400
and I want him to give up completely,

43:44.400 --> 43:46.600
I must sever his emotional attachment.

43:49.590 --> 43:51.150
I have to let him know

43:51.710 --> 43:53.370
that I already have a husband,

43:53.510 --> 43:54.920
so he doesn't stand a chance.

43:54.920 --> 43:56.520
But you don't have a husband.

43:56.590 --> 43:57.630
You do.

43:57.840 --> 43:59.480
I do, but you don't.
